#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="sn22.76"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn22.76:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 22 "
msgstr "Linked Discourses 22 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn22.76:0.2"
msgid "8. Khajjanīyavagga "
msgstr "8. Itchy "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn22.76:0.3"
msgid "76. Arahantasutta "
msgstr "76. The Perfected Ones "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli3.83, sc1
msgctxt "sn22.76:1.1"
msgid "Sāvatthinidānaṃ. "
msgstr "At Sāvatthī. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn22.76:1.2"
msgid "“Rūpaṃ, bhikkhave, aniccaṃ. "
msgstr "“Mendicants, form is impermanent. "

msgctxt "sn22.76:1.3"
msgid "Yadaniccaṃ taṃ dukkhaṃ; "
msgstr "What’s impermanent is suffering. "

msgctxt "sn22.76:1.4"
msgid "yaṃ dukkhaṃ tadanattā; "
msgstr "What’s suffering is not-self. "

msgctxt "sn22.76:1.5"
msgid "yadanattā taṃ ‘netaṃ mama, nesohamasmi, na meso attā’ti evametaṃ yathābhūtaṃ sammappaññāya daṭṭhabbaṃ. "
msgstr "And what’s not-self should be truly seen with right understanding like this: ‘This is not mine, I am not this, this is not my self.’ "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn22.76:1.6"
msgid "Vedanā … "
msgstr "Feeling … "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn22.76:1.7"
msgid "saññā … "
msgstr "Perception … "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn22.76:1.8"
msgid "saṅkhārā … "
msgstr "Choices … "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn22.76:1.9"
msgid "viññāṇaṃ aniccaṃ. "
msgstr "Consciousness is impermanent. "

msgctxt "sn22.76:1.10"
msgid "Yadaniccaṃ taṃ dukkhaṃ; "
msgstr "What’s impermanent is suffering. "

msgctxt "sn22.76:1.11"
msgid "yaṃ dukkhaṃ tadanattā; "
msgstr "What’s suffering is not-self. "

msgctxt "sn22.76:1.12"
msgid "yadanattā taṃ ‘netaṃ mama, nesohamasmi, na meso attā’ti evametaṃ yathābhūtaṃ sammappaññāya daṭṭhabbaṃ. "
msgstr "And what’s not-self should be truly seen with right understanding like this: ‘This is not mine, I am not this, this is not my self.’ "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc2
msgctxt "sn22.76:2.1"
msgid "Evaṃ passaṃ, bhikkhave, sutavā ariyasāvako rūpasmimpi nibbindati, vedanāyapi … saññāyapi … saṅkhāresupi … viññāṇasmimpi nibbindati. "
msgstr "Seeing this, a learned noble disciple grows disillusioned with form, feeling, perception, choices, and consciousness. "

msgctxt "sn22.76:2.2"
msgid "Nibbindaṃ virajjati; virāgā vimuccati. Vimuttasmiṃ vimuttamiti ñāṇaṃ hoti. "
msgstr "Being disillusioned, desire fades away. When desire fades away they’re freed. When they’re freed, they know they’re freed. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn22.76:2.3"
msgid "‘Khīṇā jāti, vusitaṃ brahmacariyaṃ, kataṃ karaṇīyaṃ, nāparaṃ itthattāyā’ti pajānāti. "
msgstr "They understand: ‘Rebirth is ended, the spiritual journey has been completed, what had to be done has been done, there is no return to any state of existence.’ "

msgctxt "sn22.76:2.4"
msgid "Yāvatā, bhikkhave, sattāvāsā, yāvatā bhavaggaṃ, ete aggā, ete seṭṭhā lokasmiṃ yadidaṃ arahanto”ti. "
msgstr "As far as there are abodes of sentient beings, even up until the pinnacle of existence, the perfected ones are the foremost and the best.” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc3
msgctxt "sn22.76:3.1"
msgid "Idamavoca bhagavā. "
msgstr "That is what the Buddha said. "

msgctxt "sn22.76:3.2"
msgid "Idaṃ vatvāna sugato athāparaṃ etadavoca satthā: "
msgstr "Then the Holy One, the Teacher, went on to say: "

#. HTML: </p><blockquote class="gatha"><p>
#. REF: sc4
msgctxt "sn22.76:4.1"
msgid "“Sukhino vata arahanto, "
msgstr "“Oh! How happy are the perfected ones! "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn22.76:4.2"
msgid "taṇhā tesaṃ na vijjati; "
msgstr "Craving is not found in them, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn22.76:4.3"
msgid "Asmimāno samucchinno, "
msgstr "the conceit ‘I am’ is cut off, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn22.76:4.4"
msgid "mohajālaṃ padālitaṃ. "
msgstr "and the net of delusion is shattered. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc5
msgctxt "sn22.76:5.1"
msgid "Anejaṃ te anuppattā, "
msgstr "They’ve attained imperturbability, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn22.76:5.2"
msgid "cittaṃ tesaṃ anāvilaṃ; "
msgstr "their minds are unclouded, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn22.76:5.3"
msgid "Loke anupalittā te, "
msgstr "nothing in the world clings to them, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn22.76:5.4"
msgid "brahmabhūtā anāsavā. "
msgstr "they’ve become holy, undefiled. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc6
msgctxt "sn22.76:6.1"
msgid "Pañcakkhandhe pariññāya, "
msgstr "Completely understanding the five aggregates, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn22.76:6.2"
msgid "satta saddhammagocarā; "
msgstr "their domain is the seven good qualities. "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn22.76:6.3"
msgid "Pasaṃsiyā sappurisā, "
msgstr "Those good people are praiseworthy, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn22.76:6.4"
msgid "puttā buddhassa orasā. "
msgstr "the Buddha’s rightful children. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc7
msgctxt "sn22.76:7.1"
msgid "Sattaratanasampannā, "
msgstr "Endowed with the seven gems, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn22.76:7.2"
msgid "Tīsu sikkhāsu sikkhitā; "
msgstr "and trained in the three trainings, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn22.76:7.3"
msgid "Anuvicaranti mahāvīrā, "
msgstr "the great heroes live on, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn22.76:7.4"
msgid "Pahīnabhayabheravā. "
msgstr "with fear and dread given up. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc8
msgctxt "sn22.76:8.1"
msgid "Dasahaṅgehi sampannā, "
msgstr "Endowed with ten factors, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn22.76:8.2"
msgid "mahānāgā samāhitā; "
msgstr "those giants have immersion. "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn22.76:8.3"
msgid "Ete kho seṭṭhā lokasmiṃ, "
msgstr "These are the best in the world, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn22.76:8.4"
msgid "taṇhā tesaṃ na vijjati. "
msgstr "craving is not found in them. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc9
msgctxt "sn22.76:9.1"
msgid "Asekhañāṇamuppannaṃ, "
msgstr "The master’s knowledge has arisen: "

#. HTML: <br>
#. VAR: antimoyaṃ → antimassa (mr)
msgctxt "sn22.76:9.2"
msgid "antimoyaṃ samussayo; "
msgstr "‘This bag of bones is my last.’ "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn22.76:9.3"
msgid "Yo sāro brahmacariyassa, "
msgstr "They are independent of others "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn22.76:9.4"
msgid "tasmiṃ aparapaccayā. "
msgstr "in the core of the spiritual path. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli3.84, sc10
msgctxt "sn22.76:10.1"
msgid "Vidhāsu na vikampanti, "
msgstr "Unwavering in the face of discrimination, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn22.76:10.2"
msgid "vippamuttā punabbhavā; "
msgstr "they’re freed from future lives. "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn22.76:10.3"
msgid "Dantabhūmimanuppattā, "
msgstr "They’ve reached the level of the tamed, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn22.76:10.4"
msgid "te loke vijitāvino. "
msgstr "in the world, they’re the winners. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc11
msgctxt "sn22.76:11.1"
msgid "Uddhaṃ tiriyaṃ apācīnaṃ, "
msgstr "Above, below, and all around, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn22.76:11.2"
msgid "nandī tesaṃ na vijjati; "
msgstr "relishing is not found in them. "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn22.76:11.3"
msgid "Nadanti te sīhanādaṃ, "
msgstr "They roar their lion’s roar: "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn22.76:11.4"
msgid "buddhā loke anuttarā”ti. "
msgstr "‘The awakened are supreme in the world!’” "

#. HTML: </p></blockquote><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn22.76:11.5"
msgid "Catutthaṃ. "
msgstr ""

